(300, 1, '2018-08-18 00:21:47', '2018-08-17 17:21:47', 'Spesifikasi:\r\nCPU:\r\nIntel Socket 1150 for 4th Generation Core i7/Core i5/Core i3/Pentium/Celeron Processors\r\nSupports Intel 22 nm CPU\r\nSupports Intel Turbo Boost Technology 2.0\r\nMemory:\r\n2 x DIMM, Max. 16GB, DDR3 1600/1333/1066 MHz Memory\r\nDual Channel Memory Architecture\r\nSupports Intel Extreme Memory Profile (XMP)\r\nGraphics:\r\nIntegrated Graphics Processor\r\nMulti-VGA output support : DVI-D/RGB ports\r\n- Supports DVI-D with max. resolution 1920 x 1200 @ 60 Hz\r\n- Supports RGB with max. resolution 1920 x 1200 @ 60 Hz\r\nMaximum shared memory of 1024 MB\r\nUSB Ports:\r\nIntel H81 chipset :\r\n2 x USB 3.0 port(s) (2 at back panel, blue)\r\nIntel H81 chipset :\r\n8 x USB 2.0 port(s) (4 at back panel, , 4 at mid-board)', 'Motherboard ASUS H81M-E', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'motherboard-asus-h81m-e', '', '', '2018-08-24 03:26:50', '2018-08-23 20:26:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=300', 0, 'product', '', 0),
